Start_Module_8986
At
Launch Pad Golf Club
, we understand that life—and golf—don’t always follow a year-round schedule. Whether you’re heading north for the summer, traveling extensively, or simply taking a break, our
Seasonal Membership
option keeps you on our roster without paying for the time you’re away.
Here’s how it works:
Stay a Member
– Your membership status stays active, so when you return, there’s no re-sign-up hassle.
Pause Payments
– We’ll temporarily pause your monthly dues during your extended time away.
Seamless Return
– When you’re back, your access is instantly restored—no waiting, no paperwork.
It’s the perfect way to enjoy all the perks of LPGC without paying for months you can’t use. Whether you’re gone for a few months or the whole season, we’ve got you covered.
End_Module_8986

Start_Module_8134
Host Your Event at Launch Pad Golf Club — Where Fun Meets Fairway
Planning an unforgettable gathering? Whether it's a corporate retreat, Birthday celebration, team-building day, or just a good old-fashioned get-together,
Launch Pad Golf Club
turns any event into a swingin’ success. With cutting-edge TrackMan simulators, immersive graphics, and group-friendly formats, your event becomes an experience.
Why groups love hosting here:
Unique, Social Venue
– Ditch the boardroom: your guests can compete in Closest-to-the-Pin challenges, scramble formats, or a glow-in-the-dark par-3 shoot-out.
Team Building, for Real
– Whether it's colleagues bonding or friends rallying, golf brings out the best team spirit.
Rain or Shine, We’re Ready
– Full indoor comfort means no weather worry—just plug in and play.
Seamless Planning
– We handle the technical details. You plan the fun. From tournaments to tournaments, we’ve hosted it all.
Tailored Pricing for Groups
– Returning groups enjoy custom rates and special perks—ask about our group packages.
End_Module_8134

Start_Module_12661
At Launch Pad Golf Club, golf isn’t just about the game—it’s about giving back. We’re honored to be active supporters of local, veteran, and charitable causes, strengthening community bonds one swing at a time.
Why We're Involved:
Champions of Community:
We sponsor major and grassroots tournaments—everything from junior leagues to veteran fundraisers—to ensure the game touches every corner of our community.
A Shared Mission:
Whether supporting veterans, nonprofit fundraisers, or youth programs, we stand shoulder to shoulder with organizations that make a difference.
Beyond Sponsorship:
Our involvement goes further with donations, organizing gameplay events, and providing TrackMan access for fundraising and awareness.
Real Results, Real Relationships:
Year after year, groups come back—not just for the facilities, but because we make their missions part of ours.
